= 1938

The world is on edge as a powderkeg had exploded in Asia, A war had begun between Japan and China. [? if austria_defeat = 1: Meanwhile Austrian Nazis have been plotting a coup in Austria, and when they overthrow the Austrian Government, they will surely invade us. ?] This year is looking increasingly dire...
